snippet.title: LONDON FIELDS Official Trailer 2018 Amber Heard, Cara Delevingne
snippet.description:
London Fields is a movie starring Amber Heard, Cara Delevingne, and Gemma Chan. Clairvoyant femme fatale Nicola Six has been living with a dark premonition of her impending death by murder. She begins a tangled love affair with three uniquely different men: one of whom she knows will be her murderer.
